title: Quiz: Identify these big European clubs from their badges | Daily Mail Online
text: Several months ago our quiz challenged you to identify all 20 Premier League clubs from a close cropped in section of each badge. You handled that rather well, but do you know your European club badges as well? How many clubs can you correctly identify when the list of possible teams is much greater and many of the badges will be less familiar? How many European clubs can you identify from a section of their badge in our quiz below? We've selected badges from across the biggest football countries such as Spain, Italy, Germany, France, Holland and Portugal.
